    "body": "Thanks for the info on the SSL cert reload. That was the big factor. \r\n\r\nOur environment does support restarting individual servers in a non-impacting fashion and there are ways to handle other stuff. The configuration reload stuff predates these newer capabilities by a considerable duration so that stuff is still around.\r\n\r\nAnyhow, I don't have a good use case now for reconfiguration support so I'll go ahead and close the issue.\r\n\r\nThanks for your time. "
